{"tid":1416702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日之後，係咪可以做全港道歉行動？","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:30:49.000Z","uid":128430,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df344096009c677a605c97ce10dcf3f53f06a845","tid":1416702,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"今日罷工，遍地開花，好多手足仆心仆命，抗爭到底。<br />\n<br />\n無可否認，今日行動的確令好多市民不便，加上政府開動輿論機器帶風向，令運動出現失去壓倒性支持嘅危機。如果我地要長期抗爭，我地事實上需要有民意做後盾。<br />\n<br />\n當我地嘅對手失去道德力量嘅時候，我地更加要有正義之師嘅形象！爛鬥爛會令人覺得我地同對手半斤八兩，失去同情和諒解。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係今個周末之前，可唔可以係呢幾日發動全港道歉行動，係各區連儂牆、港鐵站等地方，就市民呢幾日嘅不便致歉，爭取佢地諒解，打輿論戰？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反黑抗暴 光復香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"f3143ea95de6b4674ada177d414fc019c813607b","tid":1416702,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:28:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b59267f4433e2ebac0a41940f1e354e3e6ede080","tid":1416702,"uid":57439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:05:23.000Z","msg":"之前稅務大樓之後, 大家道歉完好多非連登人都由氣憤變包容<br />\n<br />\n請保持自省能力"},{"pid":"d5905532d8ec4ab7aa64ed48e8253da9c4053970","tid":1416702,"uid":57439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:29:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f60838c2b80760855578046332edcbe59f2d4474","tid":1416702,"uid":252510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:30:16.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"1713fb7dff48a423a5addb03eba8cc6215329d84","tid":1416702,"uid":252510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be Humble</span></span>"}]}